OSLO Aug 12 (Reuters) - Norwegian oilfield engineering
company Aker Solutions (AKSO.OL) said:

 * The financial outlook is sound * Sees limited impact of U.S. oil spill, but some
indecisiveness on project awards * Tender activity remains high (Reporting by Oslo newsroom)




	
